        <abstract> 
<p>Received Moritz Wagner’s essays [<hi rend="italic">Das Ausland</hi> (May 1875)] and sent him a long letter [<hi rend="doubleUnderline">10643</hi>] disagreeing with his views because they do not explain adaptation.</p>  
<p>Thanks for Büchner’s essay [<hi rend="italic">Die Darwin’sche Theorie</hi>, 4th ed. (1876)].</p> 
        </abstract>
